<subSubSection id="3C66548A55355B260B38B8552BDC9439" pageId="0" pageNumber="15" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph id="B6399C9BAB039384207F03FA03E06352" pageId="0" pageNumber="15">Diagnosis.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="49EE95741F44482D7B549C08E3477E9D" pageId="0" pageNumber="15">
<taxonomicName id="C90F4B897FEBAF134802E288C45434A3" authorityName="Ze H. Wang &amp; H. Peng" authorityYear="2022" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Primulaceae" genus="Primula" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Primula longipilosa" order="Ericales" pageId="0" pageNumber="15" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="longipilosa">
<emphasis id="8FF34B4ECA28DB2B9EAF5BE88F04CBF8" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="15">Primula longipilosa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is most similar to 
<taxonomicName id="5F5B87962C41D164B7367D1E0E339E77" genus="P." lsidName="P. mollis" pageId="0" pageNumber="15" rank="species" species="mollis">
<emphasis id="45C9C886A47B3CB3C98990C5322F31F3" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="15">P. mollis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in the long soft multicellular hairs all over the plant, the shape of their leaves and corolla. But it differs from the latter mainly in its racemose inflorescence, green calyx tube, pink to pink rose corolla, stamens of the pin flowers at 1/3 length above the base of corolla tube, and applanate globose capsule. The main morphological differences between 
<taxonomicName id="565965217714E0D57583B352AA33124E" genus="P." lsidName="P. longipilosa" pageId="0" pageNumber="15" rank="species" species="longipilosa">
<emphasis id="294A5ADBF04CBB053324B9FF4A5C3AF9" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="15">P. longipilosa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName id="E3FB300E453D311FCF44BB6D0A787DBE" genus="P." lsidName="P. mollis" pageId="0" pageNumber="15" rank="species" species="mollis">
<emphasis id="FECC290A77F9198655FCABBBFB1450DC" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="15">P. mollis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
are summarized in Table 
<tableCitation id="E31FF89FACD3D01CE5E8DEC422154AE6" captionStart="Table 1" captionStartId="T1" captionText="Table 1. Comparison of the morphological characters between Primula longipilosa and P. mollis." httpUri="http://table.plazi.org/id/9F79902A7E4A1661BF0EAB8B32CF8F26" pageId="0" pageNumber="15" tableUuid="9F79902A7E4A1661BF0EAB8B32CF8F26">1</tableCitation>
.
</paragraph>
<caption id="9F79902A7E4A1661BF0EAB8B32CF8F26" ID-Table-UUID="9F79902A7E4A1661BF0EAB8B32CF8F26" httpUri="http://table.plazi.org/id/9F79902A7E4A1661BF0EAB8B32CF8F26" pageId="0" pageNumber="15" start="Table 1" startId="T1">
<paragraph id="5C585ECCC99B8C9FF1E6698207C5ED9E" pageId="0" pageNumber="15">
